<p dir="ltr"> </p>
<p dir="ltr">Part Two/Three</p>
<strong><br></strong>
<ol>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe a home that you like to visit but do not want to live in</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe an occasion when many people were smiling</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe a piece of technology (not a phone) that you would like to own</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe a time when you gave advice to others</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe a food that people eat on special occasions/events </p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe an advertisement with a famous person in it</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe an ambition that you haven’t achieved </p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Describe a difficult thing you did and succeeded</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
